{"article_id":"LFOrXxfX86nm9FyA","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Marco Rubio has been the junior senator from Florida for barely two years ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"but he 's already considered a likely 2016 presidential contender .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"The 41-year-old Republican 's political star rose still higher this week","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"when he joined a bipartisan group of senators","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"offering a path to citizenship to millions of unauthorized immigrants .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"It 's the latest in a series of shifts on immigration by Rubio , the Miami-born son of Cuban exiles","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"who ran for Senate in 2010 as a Tea Party-backed conservative ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"rejecting a so-called earned path to citizenship for undocumented immigrants ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"which at the time he called `` code for amnesty . ''","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"`` This allows people the access","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"to make their status at this moment legal ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"if they meet certain benchmarks .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"And , ultimately , to have access to the regular opportunity","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"that anybody else in the world would have ,","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"to get a green card , ''","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Rubio said this week ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"in joining other senators","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"to announce the framework of their plan .","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"`` And obviously ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"once you get a green card ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"you 're three to five years away from being a citizen . ''","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"In a brief interview , Rubio called his reason","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"for joining the bipartisan effort","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"simple :","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"`` It 's important for our country .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"It 's important for Florida .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"And I just want us to handle it in a way","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"that 's permanent and responsible . '' `` He appears to be different things to different people , ''","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"says Rollins College political scientist Richard Foglesong , a fellow Floridian .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"`` And","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"if one looks back over his career ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"he 's done a pretty good job","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"of being what it is","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that people want him to be . ''","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"But another Florida political observer sees Rubio 's current position as a return to his roots on the issue of immigration .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"`` When Marco was in the Florida House ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"he was what you consider to be progressive today on immigration issues , ''","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"says Steve Schale , a Democratic consultant","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"who watched Rubio 's career in the state Legislature .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"`` He fought for things like in-state tuition for children of illegal immigrants .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"In a lot of ways , I think","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"this is Rubio making the full circle back to where he was on these issues 10 years ago . ''","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Rubio 's move may also give conservatives needed political cover","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"to join him .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"`` I think","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"he 'll be a great voice on immigration reform , ''","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"says Sen. Lindsey Graham , R-S.C. ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"who 's part of the bipartisan group .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"`` He 's a good solid conservative , rising star in our party .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"I think","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"it will help our chances of success greatly . ''","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"But an immigration overhaul with a path to citizenship can be a tough pill to swallow for many conservatives .","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"Emory University political scientist Merle Black says","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"it 's also a big risk .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"`` What Rubio 's done is to put himself in a position","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"where he has to explain his position ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"and he 'll have to do this over and over again , ''","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"says Black .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"For his part , Rubio waged a charm offensive all this week with conservative talk show hosts .","depth":3},{"id":59,"text":"He told Rush Limbaugh","depth":4},{"id":60,"text":"that","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"since Democrats are pushing for immigration changes ,","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"conservatives had to be in the mix as well .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"`` I know","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"this is a tough issue .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"I do .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"I know why people are uncomfortable about it , ''","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"Rubio said during an interview with Limbaugh .","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"`` It does n't feel right , to in some instances , to","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"you know ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"allow people","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"who have come here undocumented","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"to be able to stay .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"I know","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"that for some people they are uncomfortable with that notion .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"This is a tough issue","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"to work through . ''","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"Limbaugh seemed charmed :","depth":5},{"id":78,"text":"`` What you are doing is admirable and noteworthy .","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"You are recognizing reality .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"You 're trumpeting it .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"You 're shouting it . ''","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"Yet William Gheen , president of the advocacy group Americans for Legal Immigration , says","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"he feels betrayed by Rubio .","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"`` Marco Rubio , you will never be president of the United States of America , ''","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"says Gheen .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"`` Trying to stand up for illegal alien invaders instead of American citizens is a campaign killer ,","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"and Marco Rubio 's name is now synonymous with a Republican turncoat","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"trying to push amnesty for illegal immigrants . '' Such pushback ,","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"says Democratic consultant Schale ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"should not surprise Rubio .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"`` He 's a pretty bright guy .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"I think","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"he understands the risk","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"he 's taking here , ''","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"says Schale .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"`` But he 's also ambitious ,","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"and I 'm sure","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"he 's made the calculation","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"that in the long run , this is the right place to be . ''","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"Much may depend on how many of Rubio 's fellow conservatives think","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"it 's the right place to be .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":203,"left":159,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":122,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":103,"right":121,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":103,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":121,"left":105,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":2,"right":104,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":108,"